It is a good course that does a good job of introducing specific nonparametric methods. I wish we had discussed a little more about the benefit of using nonparametric methods vs parametric or the specific situations in which nonparametric methods are beneficial. The final project was a good way to experience a real lifeapplication of the methods we discussed in class.
